KDE INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
------------------------

= KDE Settings =
Change Caps lock to control.

Import control scheme into shortcuts

Go to Settings -> Workspace -> Window Management -> Window rules -> regex .* and no titlebar with Force option.
      Settings -> Workspace -> Workspace Behavior -> General Behavior -> Animation Speed = Instant

Change theme to Breeze.

Change desktop background.

Set compose key as alt gr (right alt) in input settings -> Keyboard -> Advanced tab

Delete Desktop folder and change desktop settings so that there is no desktop folder.


COMMANDS TO RUN
_______________

sudo pacman --noconfirm -Syu base-devel binutils yay bash-completion kitty rofi vifm gcc-libs poetry flameshot xf86-input-wacom kcm-wacomtablet whatsapp-for-linux noto-fonts-emoji 
sudo pacman --noconfirm -Rs yakuake okular konversation kate kcalc spectacle manjaro-hello
yay -Syu neovim-nightly spotify

${HOME}/.nix-profile/bin/rclone -v copy tdrive:/backup/data/taskwarrior/ ${HOME}/.task/
${HOME}/.nix-profile/bin/rclone -v copy tdrive:/backup/data/timewarrior/ ${HOME}/.timewarrior/
